Package civitas.celestis.math.vector

Class Long3

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
civitas.celestis.math.vector.Long3
All Implemented Interfaces:
Numeric, LongVector<Long3>, Vector<Long3>, Serializable, Comparable<Long3>
public class Long3 extends Number implements LongVector<Long3>
An immutable three-dimensional vector which uses longs to represent its components.
